videos.headline: Fromm connects with Robertson for Georgia TD
videos.description: Jake Fromm tosses a three-yard touchdown pass to Demetris Robertson to give Georgia a 7-0 lead in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fromm connects with Robertson for Georgia TD) 2019/08/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cook dashes 18 yards for Georgia TD
videos.description: James Cook takes the handoff and runs 18 yards for Georgia's second touchdown of the night against Vanderbilt.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cook dashes 18 yards for Georgia TD) 2019/08/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bulldogs dismantle Commodores 30-6
videos.description: Jake Fromm throws for 156 yards and a touchdown as No. 3 Georgia puts on a dominating 30-6 win over Vanderbilt.
